channel.title: 317 - Perfect F2P Pk source, great stable well rounded!
channel.description:
Hello, this is my FIRST release of a server i worked on a bit, I love F2P pking so i based a server off it. I hope everyone can benefit from it as much as i did Enjoy!
FEATURES: 100% Melee Following 100% Magic Following 100% F2P Magic spells 99.9% F2P Combat (2H EMOTE IS DIFFERENT) 99.9% F2P Range (Addys hit 21max suppose to hit 18s EASY FIX) Really Stable source, based off the well-known Crazy PVP NPC's with over head text with no lag at all
More Info: I've got a 2002 laptop with 512MB, I had 28 players on here MAX and did NOT even lag. [IMG]http://i299.photobucket.com/albums/mm305/sqeker07/systeminfo.jpg[/img]
Now, For some pictures!
